1. Kupila sam nove *cipele*. (I bought new shoes.)
2. Ovde je ostala samo jedna *cipela*. (Only one shoe is left here.)
3. Nisam mogla da nađem drugu *cipelu*. (I couldn't find the other shoe.)
4. Pogazio sam blato i zaprljao *cipele*. (I stepped in mud and dirtied my shoes.)
5. Volim da nosim visoke *cipele*. (I like to wear high heels.)
6. Moram da menjam đon na starim *cipelama*. (I need to replace the soles on my old shoes.)
7. Kako vam se dopadaju ove *cipele*? (How do you like these shoes?)
8. Svaki dan perem svoje *cipele*. (I wash my shoes every day.)
9. Izgubio sam *cipelu* na putu do kuće. (I lost a shoe on the way home.)
10. Posle dugog pešačenja, žuljevi su me zaboleli na mestu gde mi *cipela* pritiska stopalo. (After a long walk, blisters hurt on the spot where my shoe presses my foot.)